      • findGaps

        public List<double[]> findGaps(String code,
                      double t1,
                      double t2)
        Finds data gaps in a given channel between two times. Returns null on a Winston error. Returns a single item list with the given time span if the channel doesn't exist or if no data exist in the interval.
        Parameters:
        code -
        t1 -
        t2 -
        Returns:
        List of data gaps (each gap by a start and end time)
